the city in the midst of a series of loud, large protests against
police brutality, radical protesters are once again hitting the
streets, energized and looking for opportunity. Bill Davis passed
out Communist newspapers on Wednesday at a protest against police
brutality. He hopes to interest a new generation of demonstrators
