<SLUG> BC-UGANDA-IMAGE-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
UGANDA'S TRAUMA: A DEADLY CULT STIRS QUESTIONS ABOUT A NATION'S
SOUL 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 (NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
special arrangement only. Asian and European points: contact Karl
