<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-08 11:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0870 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v AM-NYT-BUDGET &LR;      04-08 1673
