<P>
   WEDDING-RUSH (Los Angeles) _ The busiest, most jam-packed
wedding season began this weekend, and renewed interest in tying
the knot _ coupled with a desire to marry in the first year of the
millennium _ could make this a record-breaking wedding year. By
Jennifer Hamm. (Will move in the ``a'' national news file and the
``n'' California news file.)
</P>
