<P>
   MARCHES _ WASHINGTON _ In a seasonal rite as predictable as
cherry blossoms and class trips, the nation's capital is preparing
for a spring parade of parades on a cacophony of causes. Within the
coming month, the District will be besieged by labor unionists
demanding global economic justice, gay and lesbian activists
demonstrating for equal rights, environmentalists rallying against
global warming and moms marching for gun control legislation.
(Dart, Cox News Service). 30. MOVED
