   FBN-DRAFT-NO1 _ Everyone thought that the Browns would draft
FSU's Peter Warrick with the No. 1 pick, leaving the Redskins both
Penn State linebacker Lavar Arrington and defensive end Courtney
Brown. But Brown was so impressive at the Combine and on-campus
workouts that he might supplant Warrick at No. 1. We take a look at
