<SLUG> BC-EDIT-U.N.-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
EDITORIAL: KOFI ANNAN'S MILLENNIAL VISION  

</HEADLINE>
   c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   The New York Times said in an editorial on Sunday, April 9:
</P>
<P>
   Part of Kofi Annan's job as secretary-general of the United
Nations is to think big thoughts about the future of the planet.
Last week he made the most of that responsibility by outlining an
